item.title: Cmd
item.dc:creator: @Wintercanon Wintercanon
item.description:
@Wintercanon wrote:

Step 1. Install the Java SDK (JDK).

Step 2. Add the path to the kit’s bin directory in the PATH variable (system environmental variable).

Good luck…
